channel.title: OIL — What Am I Doing (Prototype) [Emo, Electronic]
channel.description:
I found a clip I really liked on YouTube so I downloaded it, chopped it up (with varying success cause it wasn’t completely consistent in time), and slapped it into Auxy. I kinda like it.
[Here it is!](https://soundcloud.app.goo.gl/cWVVxZNs68T11xRa9)
The link to the original video is in the description of the track, so please show the guitarist some love if you check it out <3
